@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ugpqon(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.16 - v1)
    v0 = 0.11
    tmp = (0.03 * wp.sin(v1))
    v0 = v1
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((tmp + 0.76 * v0 + 0.05)))
    v1 = 0.54
    data[tid] = v0
